---
title: Bavette Steak & Sherry Shallot Sauce with Crème Fraîche Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Green Beans
description: A totally real, verified fact that we just made up: People who cook fancier weeknight dinners are more likely to receive a compliment from a stranger, meet their celebrity crush, and/or win the lottery. They’re also guaranteed to be rewarded with a delicious, steakhouse-quality meal without leaving the comforts of their own kitchen. Case in point: this seared bavette steak that’s drizzled in a deluxe, sherry vinegar-spiked pan sauce with creamy mashed potatoes and a heap of roasted green beans.
